Fannie Mae's Duncan Says Many Behind on Mortgages: Audio

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-08T13:21:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/fannie-mae-s-duncan-says-many-behind-on-mortgages-audio.html
Doug Duncan, vice president and 
chief economist at the Federal National Mortgage Association, 
says 4.5 million Americans are more than three payments behind 
on their mortgages.  Duncan talks with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and 
Courtney Donohoe on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:55
 